## Which License Should I Use?

| Use Case | License |
|----------|---------|
| Personal projects | MIT |
| Open-source projects | MIT |
| Educational/Academic | MIT |
| Internal company tools (with attribution) | MIT |
| Commercial SaaS products | Commercial |
| Enterprise deployment without attribution | Commercial |
| White-label solutions | Commercial |

---

## Summary

- **Hobbyists & Open Source**: Use freely under MIT with attribution
- **Commercial without attribution**: Contact us for commercial licensing

By using VeriPro, you agree to comply with the terms of your chosen license.
